Class Album.AccessControlList

java.lang.Object

Enclosing class:
Album
public static class Album.AccessControlList
extends java.lang.Object

An access control list. To modify Album.AccessControlList for an album, get it using Album.getAccessControlList() and set it back again using Album.setAccessControlList(AccessControlList).
